    "description": "AgroStar invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Senior Software Engineer at our Varanasi location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout AgroStar:\nAgroStar is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Work with agile methodologies including daily stand-ups and sprint planning\n• Contribute to system architecture and technical design decisions\n• Design, develop and maintain scalable software applications\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Implement new features based on product requirements\n• Ensure code security and follow best practices for data protection\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Java\n• Proficiency in Kubernetes\n• Proficiency in Agile/Scrum\n• Proficiency in Python\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Rust\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in Docker\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Provident Fund and Gratuity as per company policy\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Varanasi, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with AgroStar!",
